name: Yoyo Dodgo
description:
Yoyo Dodgo is a Flappy-Bird like game where you bounce a yo-yo, through a bunch of pipes The yo-yo is physics based, with some weight to it, and you have to time your jumps, while keeping this in mind.

This is my first game made with GDevelop, so it's a very basic game. It took me around five hours (Learning + Coding + Art) to make. I am quite pleased with the result.

Feedback is appreciated!
